<tbody>
<tr>
<td><b>Dimension</b></td>
<td><b>Review</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ease of use</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Moderate; easier for users with basic coding ability</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Quant trading depth</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Good for custom bot development</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">AI trading bot relevance</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strong when combined with AI models, external signals, or custom strategy logic</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Safety signals to review</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Paper trading, API permissions, broker setup, and order controls</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Main limitation</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Users are responsible for bot logic, errors, and execution settings</span></td>
