										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In 2026, more investors are looking for a smarter and more efficient way to participate in financial markets. Instead of relying on manual analysis, constant chart watching, and emotional decision-making, many are turning to </span><b>AI trading bots</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> that can automate large parts of the trading process.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
